-- Shanghai to increase supply of affordable housing after home price rises
-- 
-- Sun Oct 27, 2013 6:15am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/10/27/us-china-property-shanghai-idUSBRE99Q02920131027

 

 SHANGHAI  (Reuters) - Shanghai will increase the supply of affordable housing following home price rises in September, Vice Mayor Yang Xiong said on Sunday. 
 Yang also told a press conference in Shanghai that the city would crack down on illegal activities in the real estate market, without giving details. (Reporting by  Pete Sweeney ; Writing by Samuel Shen; Editing by  Jeremy Laurence )